en.name: Strike Industries FSA Dual Folder Stock
en.description: The Strike Dual Folding Adapter is the first-in-market patented system that has an intuitive unfolding system for a Picatinny interface. The Strike Dual Folding Adapter folds left or right anytime without flipping or reconfiguring the hinge. At any moment, the user can fold to the left or right side of their weapon. When moved into the folded position, there is a positive lock so the Strike Dual Folding Adapter remains folded.

en.name: JMAC ST Skeleton Tube and 1913 Folder Hinge BLACK ST-6
en.description: The ST Skeleton Tube replaces your standard buffer tube, allowing your stock to fold as flat as possible (with a compatible folding adapter). Made from lightweight, rigid 7075-T6 aluminum, it's designed for use with most mil-spec M4-style stocks and braces. It features integrated QD sling sockets that remain accessible even with the stock fully collapsed.

en.name: ISLE MFG ZenitCo 1913 Adapter
en.description: The ISLE MFG 1913 ZenitCo Adapter is an adapter that lets you mount your ZenitoCo PT-1 or PT-3 to any 1913 rail compatible gun.

en.name: NILE Silicon Carbide M-LOK Rail Covers
en.description: In order to bring you the most advanced panel covers for your M-LOK速 rail, we chose to abandon the status quo and design with innovation and functionality at the forefront of our minds. Our NILE rail panels offer the shooter an unrivaled gripping surface and excellent thermal resistance in a slim, ultra-lightweight profile (each panel weighs approximately 7 grams alone). Silicon carbide is inlaid by hand into each rail panel to provide an aggressive gripping surface but recessed into the panel itself to lower the chance of unintended snagging on nearby items such as clothing. The panels themselves are made from a heat-resistant polymer providing thermal insulation for your hands while maintaining a minimalist profile.
